About the Role: 
The Software Internship is for University students who have completed three years of their undergraduate program and who would like the experience of working in a technical internship role at the company during their study or in summer breaks between university semesters. 
Education and Experience:
 Completion of classes of three years of Undergrad program in Computer Science (or related major) Programming skills in languages such as Python, Java Basic understanding of Machine Learning, Artificial Intelligence (relevant classes and experience in relevant projects is ideal) 
